long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Instantly see if a site is built with Webflow!

This extension simplifies your workflow by visually indicating Webflow websites.  When you visit a site, the extension icon will change color to signal if it's built with Webflow.

Makes spotting Webflow sites a breeze!
